reviews.text: They have free range chicken back on supply which is very delicious.

Very local cooked food spot, that is famous for their chicken congee. Cooked ingredients are also pretty amazing, and I'm still pretty awed by the salted egg fried fish and the french beans with squid. Simply amazingly cooked. That said, the location is a little far out, and you'll probably need to speak some Cantonese to get your way around. The menu is also in Mandarin.

It's hyper local, this restaurant. Food is good, patrons highly local, and prices especially reasonable. That said, it's not easy to get to this place, and you'll ideally want to speak a little bit of Cantonese to order effectively.
Reasonable price for delicious food

reviews.text: 好多人食煙，無招呼，無酒牌又要賣酒，不知所謂
大圍食肆唔憂冇客品質一般
味道ok，份量有點少。
價錢唔合理偏貴仲成日飛單添（即是計多咗冇落單，如果埋單唔睇食咗幾錢就大鑊比多壹佰幾拾）新合發同合發同一老闆
藝術與生活如此貼近。放眼是外形獨特的藝術地標，身旁的牆壁就是藝術家的畫布。走進畫廊，任意漫遊中西藝術大師的世界；閒逛藝文聚落，發現傳統工藝與現代設計的結合。隨時拐個彎，鑽進小店裡，享受一幅畫、一首歌、一個觸動心靈的瞬間。
